data.description: Begin your next chapter at 335 Brandywine Dr! It’s a 3 bedroom home  located on just over a half an acre against a beautiful tree lined backdrop in the Penn-Trafford school district. This home  offers an open concept kitchen w/pantry, dining & living room accented by a gas fireplace. There is a bathroom on every level including a half bath as well as the laundry room on the main level. The owners room comes complete w/soaker tub in en-suite bathroom & walk in closet! The homeowner opted for the multi-use loft area on the 2nd floor but it could possibly be a 4th bedroom. Spacious finished family room w/sliding glass doors in the walk out basement along w/half bath & large storage room. Last but not least is the 2 car attached garage. Conveniently located close by to restaurants/shopping.
